input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1430,"cache_read_input_tokens":60813,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1430},"output_tokens":24,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09d2d379-4cbc-4745-9b7a-9acf62397c86","uuid":"c3d6f192-61de-488e-b399-cda482924b7c","request_id":"req_011CbxggQ2fbUmTrD4R7xmBt"},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01QRpG6PmwGoxiNehnXCovFX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01H33mx5pAYFQMa6mCVdrcdj","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Volumes/990EVO4TB/Dev/wg4/task-002-w3/README.md","content":"# Word Garden\n\n> Word Garden is a small TUI game designed as a more cheerful alternative to Hangman. It is intended as a slightly more adventurous \"Hello World\" project for testing AI-assisted software development. The game includes input validation, state management, a simple loop, win/loss conditions, and a friendly terminal interface.\n\nGuess the hidden word before the garden runs out of water. It is like Hangman, but with plants instead of gallows.\n\n## How to run\n\n```bash\npython3 -m word_garden\n```\n\nOptional flags:\n\n```bash\npython3 -m word_garden --difficulty easy    # more water, shorter words\npython3 -m word_garden --difficulty normal  # default\npython3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard    # less water, longer words\npython3 -m word_garden --ascii              # ASCII-only output, no emoji\n```\n\n## Rules\n\n- A secret word is chosen at the start. Each letter appears as `_`.\n- Guess one letter at a time. Correct guesses reveal that letter wherever it appears.\n- Each wrong guess costs one unit of water and adds a weed.\n- You win when you reveal the full word. You lose when water runs out.\n- Already-guessed or invalid letters are rejected without costing water.\n\n| Difficulty | Water | Word length |\n|---|---:|---:|\n| Easy   | 8 | 4–6 letters |\n| Normal | 6 | 5–8 letters |\n| Hard   | 4 | 7+ letters  |\n\n## Sample screen\n\n```\n🌱 Word Garden\n\n🌷\n\nWord:     _ E A _ _ _\nGuessed:  A E R\nWater:    4/6 💧💧💧💧\nWeeds:    2 🌿🌿\n\nGood guess! The garden grows.\n\nGuess a letter:\n```\n\n## Requirements\n\nPython 3.11 or later. No third-party packages — stdlib only.\n\n## Running tests\n\n```bash\npython3 -m unittest discover -s tests\n```\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1430,"cache_read_input_tokens":60813,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1430},"output_tokens":24,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09d2d379-4cbc-4745-9b7a-9acf62397c86","uuid":"6dd79bf9-9bfb-4714-94a3-af4b0122b6a3","request_id":"req_011CbxggQ2fbUmTrD4R7xmBt"},{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01H33mx5pAYFQMa6mCVdrcdj","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Volumes/990EVO4TB/Dev/wg4/task-002-w3/README.md (file state is current in your context — no need to Read it back)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09d2d379-4cbc-4745-9b7a-9acf62397c86","uuid":"ff53d3dd-7a78-441e-8037-099b7bec486a","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:50:56.226Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Volumes/990EVO4TB/Dev/wg4/task-002-w3/README.md","content":"# Word Garden\n\n> Word Garden is a small TUI game designed as a more cheerful alternative to Hangman. It is intended as a slightly more adventurous \"Hello World\" project for testing AI-assisted software development. The game includes input validation, state management, a simple loop, win/loss conditions, and a friendly terminal interface.\n\nGuess the hidden word before the garden runs out of water. It is like Hangman, but with plants instead of gallows.\n\n## How to run\n\n```bash\npython3 -m word_garden\n```\n\nOptional flags:\n\n```bash\npython3 -m word_garden --difficulty easy    # more water, shorter words\npython3 -m word_garden --difficulty normal  # default\npython3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard    # less water, longer words\npython3 -m word_garden --ascii              # ASCII-only output, no emoji\n```\n\n## Rules\n\n- A secret word is chosen at the start. Each letter appears as `_`.\n- Guess one letter at a time. Correct guesses reveal that letter wherever it appears.\n- Each wrong guess costs one unit of water and adds a weed.\n- You win when you reveal the full word. You lose when water runs out.\n- Already-guessed or invalid letters are rejected without costing water.\n\n| Difficulty | Water | Word length |\n|---|---:|---:|\n| Easy   | 8 | 4–6 letters |\n| Normal | 6 | 5–8 letters |\n| Hard   | 4 | 7+ letters  |\n\n## Sample screen\n\n```\n🌱 Word Garden\n\n🌷\n\nWord:     _ E A _ _ _\nGuessed:  A E R\nWater:    4/6 💧💧💧💧\nWeeds:    2 🌿🌿\n\nGood guess! The garden grows.\n\nGuess a letter:\n```\n\n## Requirements\n\nPython 3.11 or later. No third-party packages — stdlib only.\n\n## Running tests\n\n```bash\npython3 -m unittest discover -s tests\n```\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false}},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013CUbD4ry4mHyXAaamRvu3w","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me do a final check — verify all acceptance criteria:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":981,"cache_read_input_tokens":62243,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":981},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09d2d379-4cbc-4745-9b7a-9acf62397c86","uuid":"71be7e0f