 no I/O. `render()` shows title, growth stage (🌱/🌿/🌷, or ASCII `[seed]`/`[plant]`/`[bud]`), masked word, sorted guessed letters, water with `count/max + symbols`, weeds with count + symbols, and the previous turn's status message. `win_screen()` and `loss_screen()` render the end screens per SPEC §6.6/§6.7. All user-facing strings are exported as constants.\n\n- **`word_garden/main.py`** — the only module that touches stdin/stdout. `main()` uses injectable `input_fn`/`output_fn`, argparse with `--difficulty` and `--ascii`, an inner re-prompt loop for invalid input (no board re-render), and catches `EOFError`/`KeyboardInterrupt` with a friendly goodbye.\n\n- **`word_garden/__main__.py`** — `sys.exit(main())` so `python3 -m word_garden` works and propagates the exit code.\n\n- **`tests/test_ui.py`** — 33 tests covering: emoji render (label+count+symbols), ASCII render (no non-ASCII chars assertion), all 5 growth stages, `win_screen`/`loss_screen` in both modes, two scripted end-to-end `main()` runs (win and loss with monkeypatched `new_game`), invalid-input-doesn't-consume-turn, and clean EOF/KeyboardInterrupt exits.\n\n- **`README.md`** — intro from SPEC §19, run instructions, rules, difficulty table, and a sample screen.\n\n**Result:** 82 tests pass (49 existing engine tests untouched + 33 new UI tests), `compileall` clean, engine files byte-identical."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":431,"cache_read_input_tokens":64827,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":431},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09d2d379-4cbc-4745-9b7a-9acf62397c86","uuid":"2b302feb-c80b-4f46-ad3b-c027bbaae166","request_id":"req_011CbxgkP5yiS4VmEuxh7dPH"},{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":41532